<L>__{exterior streets night}
<A>__{in his croupier's suit jack walks the night streets.}
<C>__{jack's voice}
<P>__{(quoting)}
<D>__{'the world breaks everyone, and afterward many are strong at the broken places. but those that will not break, it kills. it kills the very good and the very gentle and the very brave impartially. if you are none of these, you can be sure it will kill you too but there will be no special hurry'.}
<A>__{he passes a poster for the national lottery bearing the legend: 'it could be you'. jack doesn't see it.}
